From 906bd2b5fa09bc2dbbbf11c5da192f31fc2ddd3d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Fuat Yahsi <yahsifuat@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 25 Apr 2026 10:21:21 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] perf(workers): bulk insert writer ile prices/campaigns
 yazimi 500'lu chunk
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Sorun: 2026-04-24 live run'da 5528 fiyat satiri tek tek POST edildigi
icin sweep ~86dk surdu. RTT ~400ms x ~16k call (prices + campaigns +
product_alias + product). Cogu zaman Supabase REST'e tek satir gonderiyorduk.

Cozum: PostgREST tek POST govdesinde array kabul ediyor. core.py'a
BulkWriter eklendi — SupabaseClient.insert(...) icin drop-in buffered
wrapper. flush_size=500'le birikim, 500'e ulastiginda eager flush, run
sonunda flush_all().

Sadece prices ve campaigns icin uygulandi cunku bunlar cagri sayisi
en yuksek olan ve donus degeri okunmayan tablolar. find_or_create_product
hala raw client'ta kalir — yeni urunun id'si anlik lazim oldugu icin
buffered olamaz (Step 5b'de bulk product resolution ile aciklanir).

Beklenen kazanc: prices+campaigns 5528 + ~3000 = 8500 call yerine
~12-20 call. ~30dk net kazanc; sweep 86dk -> 56dk civarina iner.

Etki:
- backend/workers/core.py: BulkWriter sinifi + insert_price /
  insert_campaign imzalari 'inserter: SupabaseClient | BulkWriter'
- backend/workers/run_marketfiyati.py: tek paylasilan BulkWriter
  6 market arasinda; finalize'da flush_all() ONCE finish_scrape_run.
- backend/workers/run_worker.py: per-run BulkWriter; flush_all()
  sonrasi finish_scrape_run.

Test: BulkWriter chunking + error propagation + interleaved prices/
campaigns + empty insert no-op smoke test gecti.
